var codeNode = this.document.createElement('code'),\n      domNode = this.document.createElement('pre');\n    codeNode.appendChild(\n      this.document.createTextNode(this.getAttribute('code')),\n    );\n    domNode.appendChild(codeNode);\n    parent.insertBefore(domNode, nextSibling);\n    this.domNodes.push(domNode);\n    if (this.postRender) {\n      this.postRender();\n    }\n    if (this.mermaidRender) {\n      this.mermaidRender();\n    }\n  };\n})();\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"widget-subclass"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/example":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/example","type":"text/plain","text":"```mermaid\ngraph\na application/javascript\nmodule-type: startup\n\n\\*/\n\nexports.platforms = ['browser'];\nexports.synchronous = true;\n\nexports.startup = function () {\n  const CodeBlockWidget =\n    require('$:/core/modules/widgets/codeblock.js').codeblock;\n  // const zoomMermaid = require('./zoomMermaid.js')();\n\n  function centerSvg(svg) {\n    const parser = new DOMParser();\n    const doc = parser.parseFromString(svg, 'image/svg+xml');\n    const style = doc.querySelector('svg').style;\n    style.display = 'block';\n    style.margin = '0 auto';\n    return doc.documentElement.outerHTML;\n  }\n\n  // function getStyleFromSvg(svg) {\n  //   const parser = new DOMParser();\n  //   const doc = parser.parseFromString(svg, 'image/svg+xml');\n  //   return doc.querySelector('svg').style.cssText;\n  // }\n\n  // function svg2Img(svg) {\n  //   const style = getStyleFromSvg(svg);\n  //   return `<img src=\"data:image/svg+xml,${encodeURIComponent(svg)}\" class=\"spotlight\" style=\"${style}\"/>`;\n  // }\n\n  CodeBlockWidget.prototype.mermaidRender = async function () {\n    const language = this.language;\n    if (language !== 'mermaid') return;\n    const mermaid = require('./mermaid.tiny.js');\n    const options = {\n      securityLevel: 'loose',\n      theme: 'default',\n      startOnLoad: false,\n      htmlLabels: true,\n      logLevel: 5,\n      suppressErrorRendering: true,\n    };\n    mermaid.initialize(options);\n\n    const domNode = this.domNodes[0];\n    const mermaidText = domNode.textContent;\n\n    try {\n      await mermaid.parse(mermaidText, {\n        suppressErrors: false,\n      });\n\n      const mermaidId = 'mermaid_' + Date.now();\n      const { svg } = await mermaid.render(mermaidId, mermaidText);\n\n      domNode.children[0].outerHTML = centerSvg(svg);\n      domNode.style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';\n      domNode.style.border = 'none';\n\n      // 开启放大和缩小, 拖拽\n      // zoomMermaid(domNode);\n    } catch (e) {\n      domNode.children[0].innerHTML = e.message;\n      domNode.children[0].style.color = 'red';\n    }\n  };\n};\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"startup"},"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js":{"title":"$:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js","text":"/*\\\ntitle: $:/plugins/oeyoews/mermaid/zoomMermaid.js\ntype: application/javascript\nmodule-type: library\n\nbased: https://github.com/imzbf/md-editor-rt/blob/52f9faa62b5440d8cffa8acd3a6c2b6debd7a01f/packages/MdEditor/utils/dom.ts#L126\n\\*/\n\n/**\n * 缩放、拖拽mermaid模块\n */\nconst zoomMermaid = () => {\n  const addEvent = (container) => {\n    if (!container) {\n      return;\n    }\n    const content = container.firstChild;\n\n    let scale = 1;\n    let posX = 0;\n    let posY = 0;\n    let isDragging = false;\n    let startX, startY;\n    let initialDistance;\n    let initialScale = 1;\n\n    const updateTransform = () => {\n      content.style.transform = `translate(${posX}px, ${posY}px) scale(${scale})`;\n    };\n\n    container.style.cursor = 'grab';\n    container.style.overflow = 'hidden';\n    container.addEventListener('contextmenu', (e) => {\n      e.stopPropagation();\n      e.preventDefault();\n      scale = 1;\n      posX = 0;\n      posY = 0;\n      updateTransform();\n    });\n\n    // 处理拖拽和单指移动\n    container.addEventListener('touchstart', (event) => {\n      container.style.cursor = 'grabbing';\n      if (event.touches.length === 1) {\n        isDragging = true;\n        startX = event.touches[0].clientX - posX;\n        startY = event.touches[0].clientY - posY;\n      } else if (event.touches.length === 2) {\n        initialDistance = Math.hypot(\n          event.touches[0].clientX - event.touches[1].clientX,\n          event.touches[0].clientY - event.touches[1].clientY,\n        );\n        initialScale = scale;\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('touchmove', (event) => {\n      event.preventDefault();\n      container.style.cursor = 'grabbing';\n\n      if (isDragging && event.touches.length === 1) {\n        posX = event.touches[0].clientX - startX;\n        posY = event.touches[0].clientY - startY;\n        updateTransform();\n      } else if (event.touches.length === 2) {\n        const newDistance = Math.hypot(\n          event.touches[0].clientX - event.touches[1].clientX,\n          event.touches[0].clientY - event.touches[1].clientY,\n        );\n        const scaleChange = newDistance / initialDistance;\n        const previousScale = scale;\n        scale = initialScale * (1 + (scaleChange - 1)); // 调整缩放速度\n\n        // 计算双指中心点\n        const centerX =\n          (event.touches[0].clientX + event.touches[1].clientX) / 2;\n        const centerY =\n          (event.touches[0].clientY + event.touches[1].clientY) / 2;\n\n        // 获取内容区域的边界\n        const rect = content.getBoundingClientRect();\n        // 计算相对位置\n        const relativeX = (centerX - rect.left) / previousScale;\n        const relativeY = (centerY - rect.top) / previousScale;\n\n        // 调整 posX 和 posY 使得缩放发生在双指中心\n        posX -= relativeX * (scale - previousScale);\n        posY -= relativeY * (scale - previousScale);\n\n        updateTransform();\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('touchend', () => {\n      container.style.cursor = 'grab';\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n\n    // PC 端缩放功能\n    container.addEventListener('wheel', (event) => {\n      event.preventDefault();\n      const scaleAmount = 0.02; // 缩放速度\n      const previousScale = scale;\n\n      if (event.deltaY < 0) {\n        // 放大\n        scale += scaleAmount;\n      } else {\n        // 缩小\n        scale = Math.max(0.1, scale - scaleAmount);\n      }\n\n      // 计算鼠标相对于内容的位置\n      const rect = content.getBoundingClientRect();\n      const mouseX = event.clientX - rect.left;\n      const mouseY = event.clientY - rect.top;\n\n      // 调整 posX 和 posY，以使缩放中心为鼠标位置\n      posX -= (mouseX / previousScale) * (scale - previousScale);\n      posY -= (mouseY / previousScale) * (scale - previousScale);\n\n      updateTransform();\n    });\n\n    // PC 端拖拽功能\n    container.addEventListener('mousedown', (event) => {\n      isDragging = true;\n      startX = event.clientX - posX;\n      startY = event.clientY - posY;\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mousemove', (event) => {\n      if (isDragging) {\n        posX = event.clientX - startX;\n        posY = event.clientY - startY;\n        updateTransform();\n      }\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mouseup', () => {\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n\n    container.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\n      isDragging = false;\n    });\n  };\n\n  const handler = (containers) => {\n    addEvent(containers);\n    // containers.forEach((mm) => {\n    //   addEvent(mm);\n    // });\n  };\n\n  return handler;\n};\nmodule.exports = zoomMermaid;\n","type":"application/javascript","module-type":"library"}}}
